name: ShadowStitch
desc: Destined for sacrifice, they were dressed in garments that blurred the lines between this world and the next.

name: Vial of Awakening
desc: The eyes of Apep flicker open and the Poisoned One stirs.

name: Vial of Consequence
desc: Your actions live but a moment; their repercussions never die.

name: Vial of Dominance
desc: Blood, slaves and stone.The timeless edifice of Dominance.

name: Vial of Fate
desc: Ancient myths of flame, frost and thunder. Will we ever know the way forward?

name: Vial of Sacrifice
desc: Festivities of blood. Bleeding hearts and screaming lungs.

name: Vial of Summoning
desc: Call to place the demon gods of the past.

name: Vial of the Ghost
desc: With great tragedy and power, the dead are netted in anguish.

name: Vial of the Ritual
desc: The ritual creates order. Both in the minds of men and gods. The ritual creates order.

name: Vial of Transcendence
desc: It is not our flesh, our thoughts, or our soul that limits us; it is the distinction between them.
